'''Ababius''' is a saint of the [[Coptic Orthodox Church of Alexandria|Coptic Church]]. He is the subject of a long biography attributed in the manuscript form to [[John the Dwarf]]. He was a monk of [[Scetes]]. This manuscript has yet to be translated into English.

