'''John Aalberg''' (born 14 October 1960) is a Norwegian-born American [[skiing|skier]]. He competed in cross-country skiing events at the [[1992 Winter Olympics|1992]] and [[1994 Winter Olympics]].<ref name="SportsRef">{{cite Sports-Reference |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/aa/john-aalberg-1.html |title=John Aalberg Olympic Results |accessdate=28 November 2017}}</ref>

