| parents     = [[Mohandas Karamchand Gandhi]] <br>[[Kasturba Gandhi]]
| spouse      = Sushila Mashruwala (1927–1956)
| children    = 3, including [[Arun Manilal Gandhi|Arun Manilal]] and [[Ela Gandhi|Ela]]
